slide_content_0: This guide is aimed at making the most money in wobbly life.It will show how much each job makes and how long it takes to complete. All the times listed to complete these jobs are all solo based without the help of others! Time to complete will drastically go down the more people you have and based on what job is being played.This Will Cover the Residential, City, Farm, Mountain, and Jungle areas.This will also help if going for the money based achievements:
slide_content_1: Each game has its own secrets, which can only be learned by spending long hours in the virtual world. We invite you to familiarize yourself with them right now! Here you will find information about some of the hidden objects, locations and pets in Wobbly Life, along with instructions on how to get them. Let’s get started?For example, how about getting a cool jetpack? Not an ordinary one, but a really advanced alien model! To do this, you need to get a job at a pizzeria and come there exactly at noon. 12 a.m sharp, otherwise it won’t work! After your day is over, a special timer will turn on and a UFO will appear on the location. It will not stand still, so you will have to chase it for a chance to invite the aliens to taste the delicious earthly pizza. As a reward, they will give you the coveted costume
slide_title_2: #2: Wobbly Life - How to Get Jet Pack (Alien Suit)
slide_content_2: Guide To Get The Get Jet Pack (Alien Suit) After this job starts w/o time rand UFO will appear. All you have to do just follow the damn UFO and deliver pizza to aliens. You need to start pizza job after 12am (only this hour). Once that’s been completed you'll unlock the alien outfit that will have the jetpack. How To Equipped Suit You can equipped suit in in each cupboard marked on the map.

slide_title_4: #4: Where is the Secret Waterfall Cavein Wobbly Life
slide_content_4: Where is the Secret Waterfall Cave in Wobbly Life 1. Go to the Wobbly Statue on Jungle Island Find a big rock in the shape of wobbly EXTRA. Present There will be a present behind the statue 2. The drooling wobbly It will look like the wobbly drooled so much it turned into a river 3. The waterfall Behind the first waterfall will be a cave EXTRA. Dino bottoms secret Thanks to Tingle Man, we all know where the dino is! If you need help, look below this text In front of the waterfall there is a little island surrounded by the river (the river splits in half then goes back in a whole again). Then, there will be weird noises coming from that island. Find the dino then interact with it. Controls to interact: Pc: F Controller: Y And you got the dino bottoms costume
slide_title_5: #5: How to Get Spider Outfit in Wobbly Life
slide_content_5: Mountain base Go to mountain base and find the lab with shrink ray Table When shrinked, go to the chess table, there will be a spider sitting on pizza Come and go stage Take the spider and run to place with beakers (wardrobe) Highest floor of planks Go inside hole, go to place with computer then go up one more floor Door On that floor you will see a door, take spider into door and mama spider will give you costume What I wanna tell you This took a lot of effort but it was worth it
slide_title_6: #6: How to Get UFO Outfit in Wobbly Life
slide_content_6: To get the UFO you need to go to the wobbly labs on top of the mountain then gather the parts to repair it. Get into the fork lift then move the colored crate piles and and put them in the squares that match after that jump across them and grab the battery. Find the fuse which requires a lab coat in order to get that you must first find all the missing people in the lab room you mite as well grab the keys while your at it there in the room to next to one of the missing people after you put ion the lab coat you can enter the scientist only zone then take the first right and then to elevator where you will then be on a balcony and fallow the path the the fuse. To get the fuel you must go too the formula maker up the stairs and put in the recipe corn, emerald, and purple potion. To get the keys you must go back to the lab room and you should of already seen them go to the place where the last wobbly is and the keys will be right next to him.
slide_title_7: #7: How to Get the Limo (Limosuine Car)
slide_content_7: First of all the new Tv studio has a few great features. But thats the target your looking for. Enter the elavator to next floor then enter the next elavator to next floor until you reach the Wobbly Quiz floor. Enter the room on the left thats next to the double doors for the Wobbly quiz. Once you entered, pull out the Wobbly quiz poster and then a button will be behind it. Push that button and then the elavator button for 3rd or 4th floor of the studio will be activated enter elavator again and push up button for next floor and then you will see an office for the manager I think. Enter the room and get the present and then boom you have it.

slide_title_11: How To Get Toxic Waste Car
slide_content_11: The Toxic Waste Car is found in Gooey Louie\'s home inside one of the powerplant\'s chimneys. While the Waste Disposal job is in progress Louie moves to the feeding point at the quarry, revealing a small pile of barrels. Interact with them to unlock it.
slide_content_12: Each part is found in a chest within the Temple Puzzles. The first is in the chest immediately on the left in the room the player enters after the hidden path puzzle. The second is down the left path of the maze in a dead end. The third is the opposite side of the memory pattern puzzle room from which the player enters.
slide_content_13: Take the glowing orb from the Temple Puzzles back out the start and the glowing orb from the Waterfall Puzzles into the Mining job. Behind an ore block down in the tunnels are pedestals to put both orbs. The game remembers when one is placed and when the door opens it remains open. Inside the room is a gravestone that must be put through the processor and carted away before the job timer runs out. This then unlocks the pet for purchase.
slide_content_14: Inside the Mountain Lab while small in the Shrinking Machine Lab find all the missing scientists around the room and the UFO key. Complete the middle table platforming. Zipline from the middle table to the lazer maze table and reach the other side. Complete the plank and nail platforming and reach the computer table. Complete the computer puzzle and ride the robot arm to the where the UFO key is.
